    "description": {
      "content": "The Instacart Developer Platform API is a REST-based API that allows app developers to add Instacart shopping capabilities to their websites and applications. It provides endpoints for creating product shopping lists and recipe pages on Instacart Marketplace, enabling users to select a store, add ingredients or products to a cart, and check out. The API uses predictable resource-oriented URLs, standard HTTP methods, and API key authentication, with requests made to the connect.instacart.com base URL.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Instacart Developer Support",
